data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 4 Bedroom plus a den/office home on .6 of an acre fully fenced! Curb appeal at its finest with a porch that spans the front of the home. Upon entering, you are greeted with soaring ceilings and an abundance of natural light throughout. The open floorplan is a triple split layout to allow for extra privacy. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, an abundance of cabinet space, a breakfast bar and an eat in dinette area that overlooks the backyard from the bay windows. The owner's suite is spacious with two walk-in closets and an en-suite bathroom. The owner's bathroom has dual split vanities, a soaking garden tub, a walk-in shower and a private water closet. The 3 guest bedrooms are generously sized and have great closet space. The oversized den can be used as a fifth bedroom, an office or a bonus room. Enjoy entertaining outdoors on your oversized backyard under the covered patio. This home is centrally located in Spring Hill near the county line within just a short drive to Sunwest Park/Beach, breathtaking Weeki Wachee Springs, Hudson Beach, shopping and top-rated area restaurants.
